rComments: Had Prof. MacKay twice. Best prof I've had in all 4 years at university. Absolutely fantastic. Engaged, helpful, clear, enthusiastic, always ready with an analogy. Also a great guy. If you have the chance (which I don't think you will for much longer) take a class with him. You won't regret it.

He is incredible and adorable. He is incredibly knowledgeable, and hardworking. He made me want to come to class every week. His powerpoint slides were incredibly thorough, and clear. I never had to wait too long to get back assignments. His comments were constructive, and insightful. I wish I could take more courses taught by him.

Incredibly enthusiastic instructor. He knows the material like it's second nature to him, and comes off very humble. He's not intimidating, and very good about getting back to you on questions and assignments. Very thorough.
he is so cute great lecturer. notes are amazing and the class is just fun. loved it all around. wish i still had classes like this one (and prof's like him :-))
